		rel="noreferrer"
		target="_blank">Nicole Feldl</a>);
		the role of the AMOC in the Younger Dryas/Bølling-Allerød transition; long-term changes in equatorial SST gradients;
		and state dependence in interdecadal to centennial AMOC variability.
	</p>
